In the explanation given by Andrej, he means to say that the ChatGPT is a computer programme which is able to write text based on prompts given to it. This computer programme understands English language patterns, so when it is given a starting point or prompt, it can compose a text that matches the given context. For instance, when asked to write a 'breaking news article about a leaf falling from a tree', the programme was able to come up with a comical and dramatic text on the event.